creator: Paynt
descriptionHtml:
Paynt Now is an app that turns any compatible NFC-enabled device (Android OS 8.1 or higher) into a payment terminal.

It is a great option for those who do not want to invest money in expensive payment terminals and sign long-term contracts on hardware usage.

Paynt Now app enables you to:
- Accept contactless payments that are made with Visa or Mastercard cards;
- View your transactions and make a refund or void directly from the app;
- Use analytics to see your transactions on daily, weekly and monthly basis.

Getting started with the app:
1. Get registered with Paynt;
2. Receive app login details via email;
3. Login and immediately start accepting payments.

For any queries please approach our Support team: support@paynt.com.
Read more about us at Paynt.com

It's time for Paynt Now!

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
1. Added Online PIN support for refunds. Now when issuer requires PIN for refund, the app will present PIN screen.
2. Access Frequently Asked Questions in multiple languages as presented on Paynt website.
3. Improvements of the Date filter of the Transactions view screen - user can now go to the Transactions view screen and filter transactions per date range or for a particular date by pressing twice on the same date.
